{
  "stem": "22869.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, in seven weeks, even with very little food, we were still able-bodied enough for-- for Germans to use us for whatever they had in mind.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what happened then?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they, again, marched us into the camp-- into the Birkenau camp, and they lined us up for numbering.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the transports, at that time, were arriving such in a rapid manner, they had a hard time having the people who did the tattooing-- which was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] something like-- like you to realize today somebody taking a pen, dipping it in ink, in a bottle, and making each number on the-- on the hand, by hand.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So which was time-consuming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had so many people coming in, from-- from Czechoslovakia-- they were from Slovakia, mostly-- that-- and from Poland-- from all kinds of things-- that they had very hard times to do the numbering at the speed, the rapid speed, that they want to accomplish it.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So somebody came up, just before we arrived there, with an idea to make something the equivalent of a postage stamp which is in a form that you just move a digit and every day you have a new number.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they made something like this with nu-- with a numerical system.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you could, with the tip of your pen, just move one letter and get to a higher digit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they started tattooing us so that the whole tattoo number came out in one shot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they did it to us on the chest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the problem developed later on, because the guys who did it were also, of course-- if I may say so, our own fellows, but guys who were there already.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
